as a defense [laughter].

01:12:56.720 --> 01:13:02.040
You only have to go back not
even very far [inaudible]

01:13:02.040 --> 01:13:06.910
At what point do you -

01:13:08.360 --> 01:13:11.580
&gt;&gt; Anthony Lee: I've
seen that happen.

01:13:11.580 --> 01:13:19.420
Students from Africa, I've
seen them defend plagiarism

01:13:19.420 --> 01:13:23.300
by saying that's how everything
is sort of a common --

01:13:23.300 --> 01:13:26.800
