but a common oral discourse,

01:13:26.800 --> 01:13:29.650
people circulating stories.

01:13:29.650 --> 01:13:36.930
There is no proprietary
right on who is said

01:13:36.930 --> 01:13:39.170
to own this or own that.

01:13:39.170 --> 01:13:46.310
I don't know how
disingenuous that is,

01:13:46.310 --> 01:13:50.110
but I've seen it in students.

01:13:50.110 --> 01:13:52.630
&gt;&gt; Eleanor Shevlin: Well,
