thesis or argument up front.

01:14:24.180 --> 01:14:28.370
They would take pages to get
to because it was impolite

01:14:28.370 --> 01:14:30.810
to comes -- so, it is
different cultural,

01:14:30.810 --> 01:14:34.750
but what I was thinking
with regular, you know,

01:14:34.750 --> 01:14:38.420
with another paper, I
think this is illegal.

01:14:38.420 --> 01:14:40.470
I mean, with American
students writing,

01:14:40.470 --> 01:14:42.230
